{"tid":409992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗巴士剷行人路 途人捲車底最少4死21傷(2)","createTime":"2017-09-22T13:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T15:41:21.000Z","uid":37971,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e19f55d060d94c23eb6be1380b1e20985e852b9","tid":409992,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170922/photo/bkn-20170922185210157-0922_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170922185306\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170922%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170922185210157-0922_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170922185306&h=cc53b5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人被困巴士車底。（網民Jor Lam圖片）<br />\n<br />\n深水埗巴士剷行人路多人傷！傍晚6時許，一輛巴士駛至長沙灣道及欽州街交界時，懷疑失控剷上行人路，最少造成14人受傷，有人被捲入車底，有人報警求助。消防已趕往現場拯救被困人士，救護員正於現場處理傷者，警方亦到場調查事件。"},{"pid":"497b8b77a828f6659d1f211903984bf644d8b042","tid":409992,"uid":24455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"Dc9有冇一日係唔炒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42135336e60ae8ff3a4ba2ca7cb5b081d770d13","tid":409992,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"過往討論帖子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/409777/page/40?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/409777/page/40?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"a51f9fe4bbc5a3c6b8b74c976fada2258a39a7e8","tid":409992,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"有人開左啦"},{"pid":"a2fac0313778cbe36f35e53edb95dc91e201f1ac","tid":409992,"uid":29315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:46:47.000Z","msg":"好慘，等紅綠燈就咁就過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d285329039ad82dcf10afdc681d84650ccbc961","tid":409992,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:47:05.000Z","msg"